  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Junk Signal",
      "effect": "Activate 1 of these effects (also you cannot Special Summon from the Extra Deck for the rest of this turn, except Synchro Monsters);\n\u25cf Tribute 1 monster; Special Summon 1 monster, except the Tributed monster, from your hand, Deck, or GY, that is \"Junk Warrior\" or \"Stardust Dragon\", or that mentions either of them.\n\u25cf When your opponent activates a card or effect in response to your Synchro Monster's effect activation: Negate that effect.\nYou can only activate 1 \"Junk Signal\" per turn."
    },
